    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑水城堡</strong>是一款快节奏的<strong> </strong>社交推理游戏，带有魔法的转折。多达10个陌生人被困在一个充满危险、欺骗和黑暗力量的城堡中。你会为了生存和逃脱而战斗，还是会背叛并消灭对手？ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的阵营</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>保护者 </strong>–<strong> </strong>完成任务，结成联盟，揭露撒旦教徒</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>撒旦教徒 </strong>– 破坏、消灭，并操控你的方式赢得胜利</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>被遗忘者 </strong>– 玩两面，像真正的黑马一样制造混乱 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>接近语音和文本聊天</strong> – 向朋友耳边尖叫、策划或低声说甜蜜的谎言。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/244945209a5b0b14923fb4984003da1a.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/244945209a5b0b14923fb4984003da1a.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/244945209a5b0b14923fb4984003da1a.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10个独特角色和能力 –</strong> 在讨论中让玩家保持沉默，变身为狼人，或字面上读心以揭开血腥秘密。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/93d65db29b77cab0d62db7a2bc07f1eb.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/93d65db29b77cab0d62db7a2bc07f1eb.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/93d65db29b77cab0d62db7a2bc07f1eb.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20+迷你游戏和任务</strong> – 像忍者一样切菜，像伐木工一样砍树，或在音乐记忆游戏中像中世纪DJ一样点燃蜡烛。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/be4d8dc3244a1e6038c46410cd1d8e4d.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/be4d8dc3244a1e6038c46410cd1d8e4d.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/be4d8dc3244a1e6038c46410cd1d8e4d.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>200+自定义物品 </strong>- 装备炫酷的武器、闪亮的盾牌和有趣的表情。蹲下敌人，和骷髅跳舞，或以自定义消灭的风格出场！ <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/59ae9e39912166cd6856c5b724f460f3.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/59ae9e39912166cd6856c5b724f460f3.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/59ae9e39912166cd6856c5b724f460f3.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡不是终点！ </strong>– 作为幽灵，收集灵魂为你的团队购买增强道具。从坟墓之外影响游戏！ <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/e3b86ba3a6f9f6e4b7577052e2edcccd.poster.avif?t=1763131616\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/e3b86ba3a6f9f6e4b7577052e2edcccd.webm?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/e3b86ba3a6f9f6e4b7577052e2edcccd.mp4?t=1763131616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>善与恶的永恒斗争 </strong>中，<strong>只有一方会生存</strong>以赢得城堡的胜利。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当生命岌岌可危，真相毫无意义时， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你会信任谁？ </strong> <strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/518c7dffaa72141fdb33128ac7c43325.avif?t=1763131616\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras_big/518c7dffaa72141fdb33128ac7c43325.avif?t=1763131616 width=800 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许多成员正在加入我们的Discord，以跟上开发进度。我们是一个小而活跃的团队，所以如果你有任何建议或问题，我们很乐意在<strong>Discord</strong>上与你交流。 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras/cc86cf4e350748353e4e9274c9759b4e.avif?t=1763131616\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265920/extras_big/cc86cf4e350748353e4e9274c9759b4e.avif?t=1763131616 width=800 height=267 /></span></p>",
